"that exit."
msgstr "实现会退出的应用程序有两种不同的方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/command-mode-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Implement `QuarkusApplication` and have Quarkus run this method automatically"
msgstr "实现 `QuarkusApplication` 接口，让 Quarkus 自动调用此方法"

#. type: Plain text
